@Scripts.Render("~/bundles/homeScripts")
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div id="overlay">
    <div id="overlayContents">
        <h2>Getting started</h2>
        <p>After clicking play a new round will start. The objective is to match the English letter with its Japanese equivalent. A correct match will make the selected pair turn green, an incorrect match turns the pair red and lets you retry. If you are ever stuck or need a refresher, the help button will redirect you to a page with the correct pairs for you to review before starting a new round. When all the pairs are successfully matched you will be prompted to go back to the home page or start another round.</p>
        <button id="closeOverlay" class="btn-success">Close</button>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="testContainer">
    <h2><button id="startButton" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("StartRound", "Pairing")'"><span class="fas fa-play"></span> Play</button></h2>
    <h2></h2>
    <button id="helpButton" class="btn-info">Getting started<span class="fas fa-info-circle"></span></button>
</div>

